{
  "texts": [
    "More specifically,",
    "where λ is the effective wavelength of the LSST filters (Ivezić et al. 2019).",
    "We then simulate continuum lags by offsetting light curves in redder band in time with respect to light curves in bluer bands.",
    "Finally, we downsample the simulated 30-second cadence light curve to the observing cadence of the WFD survey.",
    "The observational noise is simulated by adding random values drawn from Gaussian distributions with mean zero and variance σ 2 LSST."
  ]
}